&lt;p&gt;Community Psychiatric Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Band 6&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full time - 37.5 hours&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wolverhampton&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is for a qualified RMN who wants to develop their skills and work in the community with people over the age of 65 with various mental health needs and cognitive impairment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We have an opportunity in the Enhanced Community Mental Health Team (ECMHT) Wolverhampton for a Community Psychiatric Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a CPN you will be responsible for&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assisting in complex health assessments as appropriate and plan relevant care in partnership with service users e.g. Specialist assessment of complex nursing needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing, implementing and evaluating care plans in conjunction with service users, carers and other professionals which reflect individual need.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be able to work independently and as part of an established team, prioritizing your workload as necessary. You will have an empathetic approach to clients and carers and possess highly developed communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be expected to take part in the duty role, screening of new referrals, signposting and identifying patients in need of rapid response.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team is committed to providing safe, sound and supportive services. You will receive regular supervision, with opportunities to develop clinical and professional practice in line with service user needs and organizational values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Enhanced Community Mental Health Team incorporates Older Adult Home Treatment Team, Rapid response and generic CPN&#39;s, Psychologists, OT&#39;s, Support Workers and Consultant Psychiatrists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you think the above sounds like you and you would like to know more about the post, please contact Emma Collins Deputy Team Leader on 01902 442420.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
